1. *Žrtva* je žrtvovala svoju slobodu da bi zaštitila svoju porodicu. (The victim sacrificed her freedom in order to protect her family.)

2. On je postao *žrtva* zastrašivanja od strane njegovih vršnjaka. (He became a victim of bullying from his peers.)

3. Ona je bila *žrtva* nasilja u porodici. (She was a victim of domestic violence.)

4. *Žrtva* je bila povređena u napadu. (The victim was injured in the attack.)

5. Ona je postala *žrtvom* predrasuda. (She became a victim of prejudice.)